    title: 'Reaches Crime-Aware Homeowners',
    text: "Instagram draws homeowners comparing camera brands, studying alarm panel features, and deciding to finally invest in security. A DM from a homeowner whose Ring doorbell missed a porch pirate represents genuine upgrade intent."
  },
  {
    icon: '📱',
    title: 'Handles Alarm Emergency DMs',
    text: "Facilities managers DM photos of flashing alarm panels, triggered bell boxes, and CCTV screens showing faults. The AI responds immediately, asks about the system manufacturer and the fault display, and builds a priority service lead."
  },
  {
    icon: '🌙',
