    text: "Security concerns peak at night — homeowners hear noises after a neighbouring burglary, facilities managers discover CCTV gaps on late inspections, and keyholders receive 3am ARC notifications. The AI captures every nocturnal security enquiry."
  },
  {
    icon: '📋',
    title: 'Structures Security DMs',
    text: "DMs begin with 'how much for cameras?' or 'need an alarm after the break-in.' The AI asks about the property type, the entry point count, the existing security, and the monitoring requirement — building a survey-ready specification."
  },
  {
    icon: '🔗',
